These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: crime, documentary
1. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | documentary |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: tea, cola
1. the person drinking cola is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |
| Beverage   | tea | cola |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-3::.
City: nizza, new-york
1. the person traveling to nizza is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |   2   |
| City   | new-york | nizza |

 #################################

 
